text: Archibald Knott (2 February 1916 – 16 April 1998) was an Australian rules footballer who played for the Fitzroy Football Club and St Kilda Football Club in the Victorian Football League (VFL). == Notes == == External links == * * Category:1916 births Category:1998 deaths Category:Australian rules footballers from Victoria (Australia) Category:Fitzroy Football Club players Category:St Kilda Football Club players
